                <article id="article1"> <!-- The new article tag. The id is supplied so it can be scrolled into view. -->
                    <h2>What's a Minotar?</h2>
                    
                    <hr>
                    
                    <div class="articleBody clear">
                        <p>A Minotar is a global avatar that pulls the head off your Minecraft.net skin, and allows it for use anywhere that you can embed an image.</p>
                        <div class="center">
                            <img width="64" height="64" src="//minotar.net/avatar/clone1018/64">
                            <img width="64" height="64" src="//minotar.net/avatar/citricsquid/64">
