                        <p><strong><a href="http://ge.tt/3V2oBuF">IP.Board Plugin</a></strong> - At the moment this plugin overwrites all avatar functions making them go to Minotar. The username is based on your forum display name. </p>
                        <p><strong><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/minotar-minecraft-avatars/">WordPress Plugin</a></strong> - Fully supported avatar replacer. Based on the persons name field.</p>
